These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, rowing, handball
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, domino, bridge
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing poker and the person playing domino##2
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | handball | biathlon     | rowing | weightlifting |
| Game     | scrabble     | domino | bridge  | poker      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: london, prague, new-york, paris
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | london | prague    | paris     | new-york  |
| Flower     | azalea    | balloon-flower | marigold | amaryllis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
House: ranch-style, futuristic, craftsman, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
2. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| House   | futuristic   | craftsman   | ranch-style  | townhouse |
| Birthday           | october | june | july | september  |

