.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
House: tower, cottage, colonial, art-deco
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, mah-jongg, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the art-deco house is between the tower house and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
5. the tower house is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| House         | cottage | tower | art-deco | colonial  |
| Game   | poker  | scrabble   | snooker  | mah-jongg |

