.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, bridge, whist
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, project-manager, freelancer
1. the social-worker is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the analyst is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the freelancer is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Game   | backgammon    | domino   | bridge | whist    |
| Job      | social-worker | analyst | project-manager       | freelancer |

