.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, go, backgammon
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, raspberry, mango, carrot
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person eating mango is between the person eating carrot and the person playing go##2
3. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating mango and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Game    | mah-jongg | go | backgammon | domino |
| Food   | raspberry | eggplant  | mango    | carrot  |

