.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, turtle, frog
There 4 different types of food: pear, grapes, grapefruit, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the frog##2
5. the person eating grapes is the person eating grapes##1
6. the person eating grapes is between the person eating grapefruit and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | hedgehog | frog | turtle | guinea-pig     |
| Food     | pear | carrot  | grapes   | grapefruit |

