.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, indian, australian, french
4 different games are played: domino, go, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the indian is on the left or right of the french##3
2. the indian is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the australian##1
4. the australian is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality       | nigerian | australian | french    | indian      |
| Game   | monopoly       | mah-jongg       | go | domino |

