2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
5. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Food   | eggplant     | orange  | pepper | peach |
| Color     | purple | blood-red | lilac     | chestnut    |

