.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, marigold, bellflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy, musical, thriller
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | daisy | marigold  | bellflower | daffodil |
| Movie-Genre           | musical     | thriller | zombie    | comedy     |

