.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku, video-games, chess
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, red, orange, purple
1. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes purple is the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
4. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku     | dancing     | video-games          | chess |
| Color      | ebony | red | purple | orange  |

 